{"tid":2083754,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一家買生果 男童睹父被捕痛哭","createTime":"2020-06-29T03:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T06:18:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"300656706ca2a4e85a4e5f9f53d3fb9a225de837","tid":2083754,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T03:19:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200629/6URGRYES5NF6RYT2BIGTVKPGAY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200629%2F6URGRYES5NF6RYT2BIGTVKPGAY%2F&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8VDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=f913fa83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200629%2F6URGRYES5NF6RYT2BIGTVKPGAY%2F&h=f2f498ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200629/6URGRYES5NF6RYT2BIGTVKPGAY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n一家買生果 男童睹父被捕痛哭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_5BBugm123pMRWJ508Dz_tjldgk=/702x511/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZV5LEBHJH4VYBDCQNVH4NNRTAY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_5BBugm123pMRWJ508Dz_tjldgk%3D%2F702x511%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZV5LEBHJH4VYBDCQNVH4NNRTAY.gif&h=2f03ac54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名男童目睹爸爸無辜被捕受驚，抱着母親痛哭。Studio Incendo提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方在旺角大規模拘捕53人，當中包括到果欄買生果的市民。有男童目睹父親被拉入警方封鎖線後無辜被捕，泣不成聲，與母親一同含淚向登上警方旅遊巴的父親揮手道別。<br />\n<br />\n據網媒Flash Media Hong Kong（FMHK）報道，警方於彌敦道圍捕遊行人士，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n可以證明他們一家三口同行，從未分開，私家車車匙仍在丈夫身上。但丈夫最後仍被帶上警方旅遊巴，該名母親抱起兒子，揮手目送父親離開，並高叫着「爸爸！爸爸！」聞者心酸。母親在旁安慰，叫兒子堅強，「爸爸聽日（今日）就會返嚟」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多名長者路經被拘<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：跟蹤13日 四神秘人監視黎宅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男童母親事後受訪仍未平復情緒，她哭說他們只是路過，「我哋真係行街，揸車喺果欄買生果，然後諗住行過嚟買思樂冰」，她受訪時手上還拿着一杯飲品。<br />\n<br />\n被捕人士包括不少路經的市民，當中有不乏長者。得悉被捕一刻，有人聲嘶力竭叫喊：「我喺度落車、食嘢」、「行街都有罪呀？你叫我哋行過嚟㗎」、「我行過嚟搵個仔咋！」目送親友登上警方旅遊巴時，有人與被捕人士一同高舉「五大訴求 缺一不可」手勢，絕不向暴政低頭。<br />\n<br />\n除了濫捕，警方又在旺角<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n，但竟然被查，形容香港比內地及任何地方都恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張雅婷"},{"pid":"e31fb2ad599024cbb896569698cdee180b2a5d59","tid":2083754,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T03:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qEpj5kb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqEpj5kb.jpg&h=d66f7ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2KDBrX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2KDBrX.jpg&h=a5c2a855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Cz4w0k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Cz4w0k.jpg&h=82cb5faa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n決定前聽一聽<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8VDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=1bad539b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a>"},{"pid":"b0dc6cbf113a33b12cd987b09e7bbbd81ee9d7b0","tid":2083754,"uid":71657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T03:21:50.000Z","msg":"其實而家連馬會阿伯look嘅人都拉<br />\n證明佢地真係唔撚理咁多 拉咗先算"},{"pid":"aa0df587429f950e4c518bb747d4393cf8c161ef","tid":2083754,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T03:22:19.000Z","msg":"個細路睇到自己爸爸既未來先喊得咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣比黑警落一落名 之後一定中硬國安法 有排唔駛再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a0aed4fe40a6b26f5cb3630807a65ada08ee05","tid":2083754,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T03:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HeUgopq.